Ambipar Emergency Response provides environmental emergency response and industrial field service provider in Brazil and internationally. It offers a suite of environmental services, such as prevention, training, and emergency response to highway accidents, industrial chemical spills, and dry port emergencies, as well as services contracted through spot agreements, such as gas decommissioning, industrial silo cleaning, and underground gas tanking cleaning. The company also provides environmental remediation and industrial services; industrial cleaning of chemical and non-chemical products, and hazardous and non-hazardous waste; and consulting services focused on accident prevention and environmental licensing. It serves clients in various industries, such as chemicals, pulp and paper, mining, oil and gas, logistics, power, steel, meatpacking, cement, and other industries. The company is based in São Paulo, Brazil. Ambipar Emergency Response is a subsidiary of Ambipar Participações e Empreendimentos S.A.